brhac ca tad divyam acintya-rupam
siksmac ca tat suksmataram vibhati durat sa-dure tad ihanti ke ca pasyatsv ihaiva nihitam guhayam
naham na yuyam yad-rtam gatim vidur na vamadevah kim utapare surah
tan-mayaya mohita-buddhayas tv idam
vinirmitam catma-samam vicaksmahe
naham virinco na kumara-naradau
na brahma-putra munayah suresah vidama yasyehitam amsakamsaka na tat-svarupam prthag-isa-maninah
